<h2 class="bold font-l">There is Only One Sonic</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Defeated and facing a fiery demise, Metal Sonic refuses the aid of his organic counterpart, for in the end, there can only be one Sonic. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThereCanBeOnlyOne" class='trope-example-link'>There Can Be Only One</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
